data.text: @KellyBiden @NYGovCuomo I know. It's crazy. And then there are the forms! I'm glad you were a label get the appointments.

@DollyBelle @NYGovCuomo Yay! Congratulations. I got one at aqueduct March 27th. Closer to me. Still a hike. So happy. My momma in law is 80 and has so many underlying conditions. I am relieved to say the least. I was on that website all day. Lol.

@KellyBiden @NYGovCuomo I just got mine appointment. I went to Javits Center: Home. In the yellow box click on https://t.co/ttoB8omtrd.  Dates for Javits now start with April.  They give all the other places too. So you can just try https://t.co/ttoB8omtrd. Good luck!
@rossiyab0t @NYGovCuomo I just got a appointment at aqueduct without waiting in the queue on my phone yet had the queue open on my iPad with no luck. Weird
